:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4517:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1119587\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png\" alt=\"compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png 568w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /><br />\nToday we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible WooCommerce extensions.</p>\n<p>The WooCommerce extensions are: <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/canada-post-woocommerce-shipping-plugin/5216356\" target=\"_blank\">Canada Post WooCommerce Shipping</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/table-rate-shipping-by-class-weight-price-quantity-volume-for-woocommerce-kahanit/19352416\" target=\"_blank\">Kahanit Table Rate Shipping</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-membership/8746370\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce Membership</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and are ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Canada Post WooCommerce Shipping</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Canada Post shipping method plugin for Woocommerce provides rates in the cart, tracking information on Woocommerce orders and the ability to create Shipment Labels.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/canada-post-woocommerce-shipping-plugin/5216356\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Canada Post WooCommerce Shipping</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kahanit Table Rate Shipping</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Table Rate Shipping by Class, Weight, Price, Quantity &#038; Volume for WooCommerce Plugin is used to easily setup shipping charges based on shipping class, total weight, total price, total quantity and total volume of products in cart.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/table-rate-shipping-by-class-weight-price-quantity-volume-for-woocommerce-kahanit/19352416\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Kahanit Table Rate Shipping</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Membership</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce Membership extension allows you to sell online memberships with WooCommerce and restrict access to posts and pages on your website.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-membership/8746370\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase WooCommerce Membership</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EZejioIx82A:OXXC0NP35MY:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/EZejioIx82A\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wpml.org/2017/05/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-may-2017-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://wpml.org/2017/05/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-may-2017-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0