a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7794:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-975307\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png\" alt=\"WPML Compatible themes\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several WPML compatible themes from <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AIT Themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The themes are: <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/lorem/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lorem</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/intro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intro</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/hobby/\" target=\"_blank\">Hobby</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/elegance/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elegance</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/bandzone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bandzone</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/fitness/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fitness</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/driving-school/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Driving School</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/tour-operator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tour Operator</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes