"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Intro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Hobby</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This specialized WordPress theme for blogs allows you to take advantage of different blog post types.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/hobby/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Hobby</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Elegance</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Wedding agencies and personal wedding WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/elegance/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Elegance</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Bandzone</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Bandzone is a WordPress Theme that is specially designed for music bands.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/bandzone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Bandzone</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fitness</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This is a fitness blog WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/fitness/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Fitness</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Driving School</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A business WordPress theme, focused on small businesses</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.ait-themes.club/wordpress-themes/driving-school/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Driving School</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 styl